Package: hilda
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the Melbourne Institute's HILDA datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Henry McMillan
Maintainer: Henry McMillan <Henry.McMillan@pc.gov.au>
Description: This packages provides tools for parsing, combining and describing HILDA files.
 The package leverages the data.table package for fast, memory efficient file parsing and binding. Neither this 
 package nor it's author are affiliated with the Melbourne Institute or Melbourne University. 
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    tools,
    cli,
    crayon,
    pbapply,
    data.table,
    haven
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
LazyData: true
